        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Do I still need to ask for consent in a long-term relationship?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Yes. While the way you ask might change over time as you learn each other's cues, consent is still required. Assuming consent based on past behavior can lead to boundary violations."
